snippet.title: Kamikaze Lassplanes | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Add it to wishlist on Steam → https://store.steampowered.com/app/2253930/Kamikaze_Lassplanes/

Fly and fall for powerful Lassplanes! Discover a hand-crafted anime VN with story-driven arcade shoot-'em-up gameplay. Take part in a romantic story with drama and comedic elements set in a steampunk Kingdom filled with magic and torn by a brutal war. Decide the fate of your country and heart.

Visit http://kamikazelassplanes.com/ to learn more about the game!
